  *VERSE RIFF*  
  *Each verse riff is pretty much the same, except after the last*  
  *"9" on the G string, Frusciante plays a different ending*  
  *riff for each verse, like the "12p10-12p10" in the intro.*  
  
Main Riff: [E:-----------------------------------------------------  
  B:---10---10---10-10-----------------------------------  
  G:-------------------9-9/10--10----10----10-10\9-------  
  D:-----------------------------------------------------  
  A:-8----8----8-----------------------------------------  
  E:-------------------8-8/10-----10----10---------------  
  
