  E:-------------------8-8/10-----10----10--------------------------  
  
Ending riffs: E:------------|-13-12-10--------|--12-13-12-10----|  
  B:-10---------|----------13-----|--12-13-12-10----|  
  G:----12-10-9-|-----------------|-----------------|  
  D:------------|-----------------|-----------------|  
  A:------------|-----------------|-----------------|  
  E:------------|-----------------|-----------------|]  
  
  [E:-------------|]  
  *[B:-12p10-12p10-|]  You don't have to follow the tab exactly, I like*  
  *[G:-------------|]  to improvise and add in some slides to make the*  
  *[D:-------------|]  whole thing sound "spiffier". Sometimes Frusciante*  
  *[A:-------------|]  plays a "10p8" on the high E after the second slide*  
  *[E:-------------|]  from 9 to 10 on the B string.*  
  
