  *SOLOS*  
  *Each of the solos is easy to play, and sounds really cool.*  
  *You CAN play each solo with a metal slide like Frusciante does in the*  
  *video, but it isn't necessary, because I don't have a slide,*  
  *and it sounds fine.*  
  
