Search And Destroy  
  
  *I saw a request for this song by a friend so I figured it out pretty quick*  
  *(10 minutes) and have a pretty close approximation of how to play it.*  
  *However, the Red Hot Chili Peppers have been known to play some pretty*  
  *strange chord shapes so experiment with what I have here. As for the outro*  
  *solo, I didn't even really bother so maybe later. The intro solo part is*  
  *a rough estimation I didn't really put any effort into it.*  
